        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figs. 19–22. 19–20: Left maxilla; mp 5 maxillary palp. 19) Nesocyrtosoma hispaniolae with apical maxillary palpi securiform; 20) Tenebrio molitor (redrawn from Doyen 1966) with apical maxillary palpi rectangular. 21–22: Labium; lp 5 labial palp. 21) Nesocyrtosoma hispaniolae with apical labial palpi rectangular; 22) Strongylium atrum with apical labial palpi triangular." ;
